| c1 | c2   | c3   | c4      | bit_or(c1) over () | bit_or(c1) over (partition by c1) | bit_or(c1) over (partition by c2) | bit_or(c1) over (partition by c4) |
+----+------+------+---------+--------------------+-----------------------------------+-----------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
