with named_window
select *, bit_and(c1) over w, bit_or(c2) over w, bit_xor(c3) over w from t1 window w as (partition by c1) order by c1;
+----+------+------+---------+--------------------+-------------------+--------------------+
| c1 | c2   | c3   | c4      | bit_and(c1) over w | bit_or(c2) over w | bit_xor(c3) over w |
+----+------+------+---------+--------------------+-------------------+--------------------+
|  1 |    1 |    3 | fdsf    |                  1 |                 1 |                  3 |
|  2 |    2 |    2 | 1fdfdsf |                  2 |                 2 |                  2 |
|  3 |    2 |    1 | kkkkk   |                  3 |                 2 |                  1 |
|  4 |    3 |    2 | 8y77    |                  4 |                 3 |                  2 |
|  5 |    3 |    6 | fdfd    |                  5 |                 3 |                  6 |
|  6 |    3 |    6 | mnn     |                  6 |                 3 |                  6 |
|  7 |    4 |    2 | 6fe     |                  7 |                 4 |                  2 |
|  8 |    4 | NULL | kk      |                  8 |                 4 |                  0 |
|  9 |    4 |    1 | kk      |                  9 |                 4 |                  1 |
| 10 |    4 |    3 | kk      |                 10 |                 4 |                  3 |
+----+------+------+---------+--------------------+-------------------+--------------------+
